OL,3,CWoman who forged paternity test avoids
OL,4,Cjail
OL,6,FA woman who forged paternity test
OL,7,Fresults and lied to her ex-partner
OL,8,Fabout him being the father of her
OL,9,Fchild has avoided a prison sentence.
OL,11,FBeth Fernley, 26, told Ryan Hampson
OL,12,Fshe was pregnant and was unsure about
OL,13,Fwho the baby's father was, in April
OL,14,F2019.
OL,16,FShe then asked for #300 towards a DNA
OL,17,Ftest, before sending him screenshots
OL,18,Fshowing there was a 99.9% probability
OL,19,Fhe was the father - claiming they were
OL,20,Ffrom company EasyDNA.
