OL,6,FThe documents were later confirmed to
OL,7,Fhave been forged, Liverpool Crown
OL,8,FCourt heard.
OL,10,FFernley, of Wroxham Road in
OL,11,FWarrington, pleaded guilty to fraud by
OL,12,Ffalse representation at a hearing in
OL,13,FMarch.
OL,15,FSentencing her on 15 April, Recorder
OL,16,Fof Liverpool Judge Andrew Menary said
OL,17,Fit was hard for him to understand why
OL,18,Fshe had carried out the forgery.
