OL,6,F"This was a particularly dreadful
OL,7,Foffence which has had a profound
OL,8,Feffect on many people including, most
OL,9,Fparticularly, Mr Hampson himself and
OL,10,Falso members of his extended family,"
OL,11,Fhe said.
OL,13,FHe added: "Whether it began out of
OL,14,Fsome sort of apprehension because you
OL,15,Ffound yourself pregnant with somebody
OL,16,Fwho wasn't your partner or because you
OL,17,Fwere keen to create some sort of
OL,18,Fperfect family it is hard for me to
OL,19,Funderstand."
