OL,6,FHe said when police became involved
OL,7,Fshe continued to deny she had lied in
OL,8,Fa "perpetuation of sinister
OL,9,Fdishonesty".
OL,11,FHanding her a sentence of 13 months,
OL,12,Fsuspended for 18 months, the judge
OL,13,Fsaid: "You could not have complained
OL,14,Ftoday if I had sent you immediately to
OL,15,Fprison."
