OL,6,FGareth Roberts, prosecuting, told the
OL,7,Fcourt after he was shown the forged
OL,8,FDNA results, Mr Hampson bought items
OL,9,Ffor the unborn baby and resumed a
OL,10,Frelationship with Fernley, who he had
OL,11,Fbeen with for four years before they
OL,12,Fbroke up in early 2019.
OL,14,FHe was at the baby's birth, named on
OL,15,Fthe birth certificate and bought a
OL,16,Fhouse with Fernley in 2020.
OL,18,FShe later forged another letter which
OL,19,Fclaimed the company had made a mistake
OL,20,Fand he was not the father, the court
OL,21,Fheard.
