OL,6,FWhen Mr Hampson contacted the firm he
OL,7,Fwas told they had no record of the
OL,8,Ftests.
OL,10,FHe then contacted police in July 2022
OL,11,Fand Fernley was arrested, Mr Roberts
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FReading a statement to the court, Mr
OL,15,FHampson, 27, said he had felt
OL,16,F"profound grief, confusion and
OL,17,Fheartbreak" after learning the child,
OL,18,Fwho he had "formed a strong bond"
OL,19,Fwith, was not his.
OL,21,FHe said: "My entire world fell apart.
