OL,6,F"The emotional pain of people asking
OL,7,Fme about my daughter is unbearable and
OL,8,Fit brings waves of grief and sadness
OL,9,Fback that I can't control."
OL,11,FTom Worsfold, defending, said Fernley
OL,12,Fhad shown insight into the impact of
OL,13,Fher crime.
OL,15,FHe said: "She has demonstrated she
OL,16,Faccepts it was wrong of her, in her
OL,17,Fown words, to play God."
